These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, quad-bike, bike
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | helicopter | subway | quad-bike | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia, rose, dahlia
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Flower   | zinnia | bellflower | dahlia | rose |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, siglo, montecristo, aristoff
1. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the chaman-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar   | chaman | montecristo | siglo | aristoff |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, coral, pink, white
1. the person who likes pink is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes white##1
3. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Color   | coral | black | white | pink |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, february, may, january
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Birthday   | january | may | february | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-6::.
