3. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3   |   4    |
| City   | boston | london | berlin | venice |

