.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, juice, fanta
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | fanta | coffee | iced-tea | juice |

